      "text": [
        "2145 - وَ قَالَ اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : «اَلنَّظَرُ إِلَى عَلِيٍّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ عِبَادَةٌ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2145 - The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him and his family, said: \"Looking at Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) is an act of worship.\""
        ]
      }
    }
